# Dev and Build Commands

- **Do not run** dev servers or build commands (e.g. `pn dev`, `npm run dev`, `pnpm dev`, `vite`, `pn build`, `npm run build`, `pnpm build`).
- **Assume** the dev server and build tooling are already running or will be started by the user.
- When suggesting verification steps, tell the user to check the app in the browser or rely on their existing dev/build process instead of running these commands in the agent.
